### ================= Admin System Tests =================
### 1. Admin login
### Copy access_token from response and paste it into @admin_token below.

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123456"
}

###
@admin_token = paste_admin_access_token_here
@user_id = 1


### 2. Dashboard statistics

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/dashboard/statistics
Accept: application/json


### ================= Marketplace Tests =================
### Requires normal user token.

@market_user_token = paste_normal_user_token_here
@market_admin_token = paste_admin_access_token_here
@expert_id = 1
@expert_order_id = 1
@community_post_id = 1
@candidate_id = 1


### Apply expert

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/expert/apply
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_user_token}}

{
  "name": "张老师",
  "title": "国学命名专家",
  "description": "从业10年，擅长宝宝起名与传统文化分析。",
  "tags": ["国学", "宝宝起名"],
  "price": 199,
  "experience_years": 10
}


### Admin list pending experts

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/experts?status=pending
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_admin_token}}


### Admin approve expert

PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/experts/{{expert_id}}/approve
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_admin_token}}


### List approved experts

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/experts?page=1&page_size=10
Accept: application/json


### Expert detail

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/experts/{{expert_id}}
Accept: application/json


### Create expert order

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/expert-orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_user_token}}

{
  "expert_id": {{expert_id}},
  "name_record_id": null
}


### Expert workbench orders

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/expert/orders
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_user_token}}


### Submit expert report

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/expert/orders/{{expert_order_id}}/report
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_user_token}}

{
  "summary": "该名称整体传播性较强。",
  "analysis": "音形义较协调，适合商业品牌使用。",
  "suggestions": "建议同步查询商标与域名，并建立统一视觉规范。"
}


### User view expert order/report

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/expert-orders/{{expert_order_id}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_user_token}}


### Create community vote post

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/community/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_user_token}}

{
  "title": "帮我选一个AI公司名称",
  "description": "做AI硬件创业",
  "candidates": ["智穹科技", "未来智联", "穹界智能"]
}


### List community posts

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/community/posts?sort=latest&page=1&page_size=10
Accept: application/json


### Community post detail

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/community/posts/{{community_post_id}}
Accept: application/json


### Vote community candidate

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/community/posts/{{community_post_id}}/vote
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{market_user_token}}

{
  "candidate_id": {{candidate_id}}
}


### Community result

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/community/posts/{{community_post_id}}/result
Accept: application/json


### Community rank

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/community/rank
Accept: application/json


### ================= Brand Visual Image Tests =================
### Requires normal user token, not admin token.
### Copy token from /auth/login response.

@user_token = paste_normal_user_token_here
@brand_visual_record_id = 1


### Generate brand visual text plan

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/brand/visual/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "name": "智穹科技",
  "industry": "人工智能硬件",
  "style": "科技感、未来感、高端",
  "meaning": "智能连接未来，探索无限可能",
  "target_users": "AI硬件创业团队",
  "usage_scene": "官网、名片、融资BP、社交媒体"
}


### Generate logo image from logo_prompt
### Paste logo_prompt from previous response below.

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/brand/visual/image
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

{
  "record_id": {{brand_visual_record_id}},
  "logo_prompt": "为中文品牌“智穹科技”设计一张高质量Logo概念图，科技感、未来感、高端，蓝银配色，简洁几何符号，适合AI硬件品牌。",
  "size": "1024*1024",
  "n": 1
}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 3. List normal users - page 1

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/users?page=1&page_size=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 4. Search normal users by email or username

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/users?page=1&page_size=10&keyword=1227869890
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 5. Get normal user detail

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/users/{{user_id}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 6. Disable normal user

PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/users/{{user_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "disabled"
}


### 7. Enable normal user

PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/users/{{user_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "active"
}


### 8. List name records - reserved interface
### The project currently has no standalone name record table, so items is expected to be [].

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/name-records?page=1&page_size=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 9. Filter name records - reserved interface

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/name-records?page=1&page_size=10&user_id={{user_id}}&naming_type=company&keyword=AI
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}


### 10. Verify normal user token cannot access admin API
### Replace the token below with a normal /auth/login token. Expected: 403.

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/dashboard/statistics
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer paste_normal_user_token_here


### 11. Verify missing admin token is rejected
### Expected: 403 Not authenticated.

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/dashboard/statistics
Accept: application/json
